* Manage\nVolume Permissions
** Key privileges
***_ READ VOLUME: list and read files
***_ WRITE VOLUME: create, update, delete files
***_ CREATE VOLUME: create new volumes
***_ CREATE EXTERNAL VOLUME
** Grant using SQL
***_ GRANT READ VOLUME ON VOLUME ... TO group
** Permission inheritance
***_ Cascade from parent catalog/schema
** No folder-level ACLs
***_ Permissions apply to whole volume
***_ Use separate volumes for different access
** Users also need USE CATALOG and USE SCHEMA
@endmindmap
